CTM BusFinder is the Official App of CTM SpA that guides you during your trips in the Area of Cagliari.

Through the App, CTM does not access to any of your  personal data stored in the device.

With CTM BusFinder you can:
- Read the last news retrieved from the CTM site and Twitter account;
- See the route of the bus lines on the map with the list of bus stops and schedules;
- Plan your journey to reach your destinations  and see the details about the relevant bus stops;
- See the bus stops around you or in a selected area of interest;
- Consult the real-time data about the next bus transits and the relevant routes with reference to a bus stop of interest, also using a QR code reader; 
- See the list of ticket shops around you or in a selected area of interest;
- Manage a list of preferred bus stops for a quick access;
- Purchase CTM single and season electronic tickets;
- Validate electronic tickets by scanning QR codes in CTM buses.

